    SwingVoltageUpdateRec, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class SwingVoltageUpdateRecImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl
implements SwingVoltageUpdateRec
    An implementation of the model object 'Swing Voltage Update Rec'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Remote Node Id
    • Aclf Net Id
    • Aclf Net Name
    • Swing Bus Id
    • VMag
    • VAng
